Titolo: Mystic Warriors

Anno: 1993

Descrizione: Mystic Warriors: Wrath of the Ninjas (ミスティックウォリアーズ -怒りの忍者-, Mystic Warriors - Ikari no Ninja) is a ninja-themed side-scrolling shoot-'em-up released as a coin-operated video game by Konami in 1993. It was developed by the same team that also produced the earlier arcade game, western-themed Sunset Riders, and features similar gameplay to its predecessor.